{"tid":1346830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"22/7 消息：村民收消息下午3時至10時避去元朗市區","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:27:53.000Z","uid":207600,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"aee08d802441af859da3fe93f994126ecf5f8859","tid":1346830,"uid":207600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"【元朗黑夜】消息：村民收溫提　下午3時至10時避去元朗市區<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/354725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F354725&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=fb9b26d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/354725</a><br />\n有村民今早（22日）再收到「溫馨提示」，呼籲今天下午3時至晚上10時不要去元朗市區，料有大型事件將會發生。消息指，元朗多條村的原居民村代表通知村民，今日盡量不要外出到元朗市區。消息形容，村代表幾乎「傾盤而出」地不停呼籲村民留守家中以保安全，今早更以打電話、發訊息及錄音等途徑廣發消息，似暗示今日會比昨日更大件事。該「溫馨提示」指，「講明有工具供應，見著黑衫戴口罩，勢必上前行動。」"},{"pid":"ca66d7e3b90857fc11d4ac5794c3d6b807258811","tid":1346830,"uid":207600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:54:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9c0f5945f4f741c6306afcd1ebc94a2ab86965a","tid":1346830,"uid":207600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cb8ae214985f3c2af86d0a658e90bb77460d91c","tid":1346830,"uid":207600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:55:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df471f70c934c4d7a6988fabb5b3d37e71fb95c2","tid":1346830,"uid":186431,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:58:19.000Z","msg":"黑社會統治香港，元朗宣布獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ad68f6c7f13fb672c74a6905842575f39b5598","tid":1346830,"uid":138116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:58:48.000Z","msg":"夠薑就出嚟打人囉"},{"pid":"7ae695c954ca66a67319f806a150ce32dcf483ee","tid":1346830,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c